{"tid":1027581,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"求救，懷疑底版intel lan壞左","createTime":"2019-02-19T01:51:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T01:04:23.000Z","uid":50062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e511099a8cfed4538e5ef2e53f5ab7b5f11ac2ec","tid":1027581,"uid":50062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T01:51:53.000Z","msg":"Spec：<br />\nz270f <br />\ni7-7700k<br />\nNetgear R800<br />\nNetgear R7000<br />\n新買兩條cat6 5m<br />\n屋內cat5<br />\n<br />\n症狀：<br />\nDevice manager 認到張intel connection 1912，但auto連線速度只用到100mb, 手動轉1gb 全雙工就上唔到網<br />\n<br />\n己試：<br />\n換cable線<br />\n換router/換port/直連modem<br />\n重裝intel lan driver<br />\nintel proset diagnostics (有一項failed)<br />\nrouter 己關閉Qos, access control, auto ip, auto dns<br />\n<br />\n最後就係試驗途中為左方便router 同 cable 係拉長放左係地下而唔係平時族router個位果陣，試過去到3xx~4xx mb，一放原位又跌做幾十mb，會唔會有機會係底版果邊接觸不良或者壞lan?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a5aafa1e3b48d97314c2628a4ad3125441d4f5","tid":1027581,"uid":122394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T03:22:20.000Z","msg":"放落地下就一定有400mb ？<br />\n定係都係一時時"},{"pid":"ac3aaf1d86609add2f67581e58f969822f1af20a","tid":1027581,"uid":122394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T03:30:48.000Z","msg":"同埋你係突然間咁定係郁過部機/其它野？"},{"pid":"f36b3a83d9a591479cb35958eabb5026610f3678","tid":1027581,"uid":147767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T03:32:46.000Z","msg":"仲有PCIe lan card未試"},{"pid":"d355fb077aeed4c4a142fe3e5291b1ff8e8cfa7b","tid":1027581,"uid":50062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7a5aafa1e3b48d97314c2628a4ad3125441d4f5","tid":1027581,"uid":122394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T03:22:20.000Z","msg":"放落地下就一定有400mb ？<br />\n定係都係一時時"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T05:11:18.000Z","msg":"一時時 每次我由枱底拉個router 同堆線出黎整好耐 